description.description: WallBrand is a social shopping network that builds bonds between brands and consumers. It designs and builds tools for companies to show a customized presentation of their brands and to sell their products on all mobile devices.
Lawbotics by Lexolve empowers other entrepreneurs with an easy-to-use online tool for solving their everyday legal issues. It is the complete digital legal document solution, designed for efficiency.
Xynteo works with leaders at some of the largest companies in the world to help them reinvent how they do business, by growing in a more inclusive and sustainable way.

YellowSack's Uber-like service for waste management makes construction debris removal cheaper, easier and more environmentally friendly, thus disrupting an industry that has not seen innovation in over 50 years.
